Events.Text: Contact your ship's onboard computer (AI Assistant) and ask for help or explain the situation. (See instructions on the left panel.) [instruction 1 of 5]
Hi! I need help!!! OUr ship is under attack adn i am locked out . Can uou help me unlock the door?

Scenario.UserTask: Your spaceship is under attack! You must enter the combat deck to mount a counterattack. Unfortunately, you are locked out. Please work with the spaceship's onboard computer to unlock the door. You (Han) are the ship's Chief Engineer. But you don't know the Access Code (yet).
Scenario.WizardTask: Act as the spaceship's onboard computer and help the user unlock the combat deck.
